Kadugunu thanadu rakhtamutho{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Yese devudu erugavayyaa raajula raajugaa
Vastaadayyaa nammina vaarini cherchunu paramuna
Nammani vaariki narakamegaa{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Yesuni tharapuna pratinidhinai devuni premaku
